<bibRefCitation author="Ivanenko, V. N. &amp; Martinez Arbizu, P. &amp; Stecher, J." box="[679,1087,1449,1475]" pageId="19" pageNumber="320" pagination="1 - 21" refId="ref16781" refString="Ivanenko, V. N., Martinez Arbizu, P. &amp; Stecher, J. (2006) Copepods of the family Dirivultidae (Siphonostomatoida) from deepsea hydrothermal vent fields on the Mid-Atlantic Ridge at 14 ºN and 5 ºS. Zootaxa, 1277 (1), 1 - 21. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 1277.1.1" type="journal article" year="2006">Ivanenko and Martinez Arbizu 2006</bibRefCitation>
